dct_title_s: Tabula geographica in qva regiones Cananææ, et locorum situs prout ea tempore Christi, et Apostolorum fuerunt de integro describuntur, ac suis Limitibus distinguntur

dct_description_sm: auctore D.R.M. Mathes ; gedruckt t Amstelredam by Jan Evertss Cloppenborch.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
2 bar scales on map given in "Miliaria germanica" and "Leucae horariae".
Features illustrations of a ship and compass rose.
Shows topography, drainage, territorial boundaries of the tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
